5. c3 Qc7 6. h3 g6 7. Qc2 $6 {This prophylactic move is wrong here.} (7. Ne2
Bf5 8. Bxf5 gxf5 {typical structure with gxf5 (Dominguez-Mamedyarov)}) 7... f6
$1 {without the knight on f6, this move is now strong, preparing ...e7-e5.
White does not have a good way of stopping it.} 8. Ne2 (8. f4 {[#]} Nh6 $1 9.
