A speculative sacrifice that did not work out.} (11. Qa4 {[%cal Gd3c2]} Bf5 $11
) 11... e4 12. Bxe4 dxe4 13. Nbc3 Bg7 14. Nd5 Qd6 15. Bf4 Be5 16. Rad1 Bxf4 17.
