Bxb4 21. h6 (21. hxg6 axb2 22. Bxf6 gxf6 $17) 21... Re8 22. hxg7 Nd7 {Black
king is safe as the g7-pawn is bound to fall.} 23. Rb3 Be7 24. Rc3 Qb7 $15 0-1

