10... Nxe4 {This is the most accurate because it allows Black to win an
important tempo to fight for d4-square.} ({In the event of} 10... O-O 11. c3
Nxe4 12. Qxe4 Bf6 13. d4 Nd7 $14 {we have a typical position where White has a
